
        +: positive
        -: negative
        ++: increment
        --: decrement
        + -: ===> -
        - - :===> +
        + + :===> +

    increment : increases the value by 1

    increment are :
                1. pre increment;
     operator is placed before the variable;
                 2. post increment
          operator after the variable


    decrement: decreases the value by 1


